description: A wrapper for calls to Microsoft Graph using Managed Identity.
releaseNotes: Due to IDE warning[s], array was not set on the collections for submission to Microsoft Graph, so we received a 400 Bad Request, "The request is malformed or incorrect. Expected array for value of property: Collection(microsoft.graph.tiIndicator)". Explicit Array is now set on both collections used to push Threat Intelligence Indicators to Microsoft Graph.
